FuncDecl.Name: GuiBindableTreeView
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Create a bindable Tree view control.</summary> <param name="_styleProvider">The style provider for this control.</param> <param name="_itemSource">The item source.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: SetItemSource
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Set the item source.</summary> <param name="itemSource">The item source. Null is acceptable if you want to clear all data.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: GetTextProperty
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Get the text property name to get the item text from an item.</summary> <returns>The text property name.</returns> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: SetTextProperty
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Set the text property name to get the item text from an item.</summary> <param name="value">The text property name.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: GetImageProperty
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Get the image property name to get the image from an item.</summary> <returns>The image property name.</returns> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: SetImageProperty
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Set the image property name to get the image from an item.</summary> <param name="value">The image property name.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: GetChildrenProperty
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Get the children property name to get the children from an item.</summary> <returns>The children property name.</returns> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: SetChildrenProperty
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Set the children property name to get the children from an item.</summary> <param name="value">The children property name.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: GetSelectedItem
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Get the selected item.</summary> <returns>Returns the selected item. If there are multiple selected items, or there is no selected item, null will be returned.</returns> </Document>
